<body>
  <%- include('../partials/header') %>

  <main class="legal-page">
    <h1><span class="ca-flag">üêª</span> California Age & AI Transparency Notice</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: December 2024 (CPRA Compliant)</p>

    <div class="highlight">
      <p><strong>For California Residents.</strong> This notice supplements our Privacy Policy pursuant to the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) as amended by the California Privacy Rights Act (CPRA), effective January 1, 2023, and California's Age-Appropriate Design Code (effective July 2024).</p>
    </div>

    <h2>1. CPRA Consumer Rights (2024-2025)</h2>
    <p>As a California resident, you have the following rights under CPRA:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Right to Know:</strong> Learn what personal information we collect, use, disclose, and sell</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Delete:</strong> Request deletion of your personal information</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Correct:</strong> Correct inaccurate personal information</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Opt-Out:</strong> Opt out of the sale or sharing of personal information</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Limit:</strong> Limit the use of sensitive personal information</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Non-Discrimination:</strong> Not be discriminated against for exercising your rights</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. "Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information"</h2>
    <div class="opt-out-box">
      <p><strong>Your Right to Opt Out</strong></p>
      <p>GetPawsy does not "sell" personal information in the traditional sense. However, we may "share" information with advertising partners for targeted advertising, which qualifies as "sharing" under CPRA.</p>
      <p><strong>To Opt Out:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email us at: <strong>privacy@getpawsy.com</strong> with subject "Do Not Sell/Share"</li>
        <li>We will process your request within 15 business days</li>
        <li>Your opt-out applies to future data sharing only</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>3. Minors' Data Protection</h2>
    <p>GetPawsy takes the protection of minors' data seriously:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Age Restriction:</strong> Our services are intended for users 16 years of age and older</li>
      <li><strong>No Knowing Collection:</strong> We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13</li>
      <li><strong>Parental Consent:</strong> For users 13-15, we require parental consent before collecting personal information</li>
      <li><strong>Opt-In Required:</strong> We do not sell or share data of consumers under 16 without affirmative authorization</li>
    </ul>
    <p>If you believe we have collected data from a minor without appropriate consent, please contact us immediately at <strong>privacy@getpawsy.com</strong>.</p>

    <h2>4. AI Transparency Notice</h2>
    <div class="ai-box">
      <p><strong>ü§ñ Automated Decision-Making Disclosure</strong></p>
      <p>GetPawsy uses artificial intelligence and automated decision-making in the following ways:</p>
    </div>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Product Recommendations:</strong> AI analyzes browsing and purchase history to suggest products you may like</li>
      <li><strong>Pawsy AI Chatbot:</strong> AI-powered customer support assistant provides automated responses</li>
      <li><strong>Dynamic Pricing:</strong> AI may adjust promotional offers based on market conditions (not based on individual consumer characteristics)</li>
      <li><strong>Fraud Detection:</strong> Automated screening identifies potentially fraudulent transactions</li>
      <li><strong>Email Personalization:</strong> AI helps personalize marketing email content</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Your AI Rights</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Opt-Out of Profiling:</strong> You may opt out of AI-powered profiling for advertising purposes</li>
      <li><strong>Request Human Review:</strong> For significant decisions, you may request a human review</li>
      <li><strong>Access Logic:</strong> You may request information about the logic involved in automated decisions</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Behavioral Advertising Opt-Out</h2>
    <p>To opt out of behavioral advertising:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Browser Settings:</strong> Enable "Do Not Track" in your browser</li>
      <li><strong>Cookie Preferences:</strong> Adjust your cookie settings on our website</li>
      <li><strong>Industry Opt-Out:</strong> Visit <a href="https://optout.aboutads.info" target="_blank" rel="noopener">optout.aboutads.info</a></li>
      <li><strong>Email Us:</strong> Send request to privacy@getpawsy.com</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Sensitive Personal Information</h2>
    <p>We may collect the following sensitive personal information:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Precise geolocation (for shipping purposes only)</li>
      <li>Account login credentials (stored securely with encryption)</li>
      <li>Payment card information (processed by secure third-party processors)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You have the right to limit the use and disclosure of sensitive personal information to what is necessary to perform our services.</p>

    <h2>7. Contact for California Privacy Rights</h2>
    <p>To exercise your California privacy rights:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> privacy@getpawsy.com</li>
      <li><strong>Subject Line:</strong> California Privacy Request</li>
      <li><strong>Response Time:</strong> 45 days (may be extended by 45 additional days if necessary)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We will verify your identity before processing any request. You may designate an authorized agent to make a request on your behalf.</p>

    <h2>8. Annual Statistics</h2>
    <p>In compliance with CPRA, we publish annual statistics on consumer requests (available upon request after January 1 each year).</p>
  </main>

  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
